inst/include/half/half.hpp
--------------------------
A verbatim copy of half.hpp version 2.2.0, the IEEE 754-based half-precision
floating-point library by Christian Rau. It provides the C++ `half` type used
for host-side f16 (binary16) buffer conversion and printing.

